  </refsynopsisdiv>
  <refsect1 id="description">
   <title>DESCRIPTION</title>
   <para>Check the status of a RedHat Cluster Suite Cluster by parsing the 
     output of clustat and <filename>/etc/cluster/cluster.conf</filename>.</para>
   <para>Status and location of each service is checked and compared with
     the values from cluster.conf.</para>
